data.description: Welcome to your future home! This delightful half duplex, located in the heart of Fords, NJ, offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Boasting 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom, this property is an ideal choice for first-time homebuyers, small families, or those looking to downsize.  This home features two cozy bedrooms, providing ample space for relaxation and personalization.  Enjoy the convenience of a full bathroom, designed with functionality and style in mind.  The property offers parking space for up to 4 cars, ensuring that you and your guests always have a convenient place to park.  Stay warm and comfortable throughout the seasons with the central heating system, providing efficient and reliable warmth.  The roof, installed just over 10 years ago, provides both durability and peace of mind. You can trust that your home is well-protected from the elements.  Beneath your feet, discover the timeless elegance of hardwood floors. Not only are they visually appealing, but they also add a touch of warmth and character to the living spaces. Situated in Fords, NJ, this property enjoys a prime location with access to local amenities, schools, and parks. The neighborhood offers a welcoming community atmosphere and convenient proximity to shopping centers and dining options.
